{"tid":1029572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國業界推美容年輕化　7歲女童：每天上學前都會化妝","createTime":"2019-02-20T10:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T04:30:26.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb8e9ebbba446a2e7f9b0f7f0f2b4a71eaaf483","tid":1029572,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190220/s00005/65bd9efaa5fff1b47d487e80b8f0efcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190220%2Fs00005%2F65bd9efaa5fff1b47d487e80b8f0efcb.jpg&h=00f5526d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國有美容公司開設服務女童的美容院，讓4到10歲的女童一嘗美容、敷面膜、化妝及美甲的滋味。有人擔心美容業年輕化，會令女孩失去童真。<br />\n<br />\n韓國美容業出現年輕化趨勢，近日多間公司推出針對年幼女孩的美容產品，標榜化妝品「更健康」，包括女童用的面膜、水溶性指甲油及無毒性唇膏等等。更有公司成立女孩美容院，讓她們可享受足浴、按摩、美甲及化妝等服務，療程價格由折合150到250港元不等。<br />\n<br />\n美容在韓國女童間漸趨流行，當地兒童美容業正快速擴展。據《華盛頓郵報》報道，7歲女童楊慧智（譯音）表示，自己每天上學前都會化妝，更兩度前往位於首爾的女孩美容院。有女童於網上上傳片段，介紹自己的小學化妝習慣。亦有針對女孩的化妝品公司，在廣告中引述女童的話：「我看着媽媽化妝，我現在模仿她，我已經長大了。」<br />\n<br />\n一項2016年的調查發現，四成二受訪女生由小學開始已有化妝習慣，相信趨勢會持續上升。有專家擔心，美容年輕化會令女孩對自己的外表失去信心，批評推出針對女童的產品，是美容業的賺錢手段。<br />\n<br />\n韓國對女性的審美標準狹窄，近年為人詬病。早前有女性發起「解開腰束」的運動，將化妝品毀棄，以素顏示人，以帶出女性不一定要跟隨社會主流審美標準。<br />\n<br />\n（華盛頓郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190220/s00005/1550654130083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190220%2Fs00005%2F1550654130083&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n83jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=01ff18c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190220%2Fs00005%2F1550654130083&h=9a36d28f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190220/s00005/1550654130083</a>"},{"pid":"6f828e30648bff223c8ce2fbc7748061179497d4","tid":1029572,"uid":142313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"推行多幾年大家都會習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b4e268b6b771ef7876f9c7916cb3ac0f5c1193","tid":1029572,"uid":143499,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家價值觀錯曬<br />\n<br />\n政治又係咁經濟又係咁社會階級觀念都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講乜嘢南韓有民主， 要講臭蟲論大把衰國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061a0be9c2372d496b1a4730a24079b63dbed93c","tid":1029572,"uid":165336,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"根本18歲前都唔應該化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十幾歲係最青春最可愛皮膚最靚既年紀,<br />\n化妝只會令佢地變到同d殘花敗柳易容術一樣咁既膠樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲會令皮膚變差,更加快令個樣變成唔化妝唔得"},{"pid":"f51b2c2d682c3947662aaf8d5b3a9e764fc41d84","tid":1029572,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:56:54.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"0ef12aff21c4c9d2381a4dbc4ec990f0206c064d","tid":1029572,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"17歲之後塊面再上唔到粧"},{"pid":"51f06610e82134fdc9cde0091363c8ba82aa0108","tid":1029572,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"On lun 9"},{"pid":"aad7e17000d3d57c92cedfba6fff162a4db478f6","tid":1029572,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"061a0be9c2372d496b1a4730a24079b63dbed93c","tid":1029572,"uid":165336,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"根本18歲前都唔應該化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十幾歲係最青春最可愛皮膚最靚既年紀,<br />\n化妝只會令佢地變到同d殘花敗柳易容術一樣咁既膠樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲會令皮膚變差,更加快令個樣變成唔化妝唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"前幾日去首爾旅行，尋日回港。<br />\n行明洞、新沙洞林蔭大道同弘大附近。好撚多後生女化晒妝行街。<br />\n聽導遊講當地女仔化妝返學老師係唔會鬧，返學/行街會帶CC Cream、唇膏同粉餅。"},{"pid":"a32963dac02655d221de5b589d064d3a03d84996","tid":1029572,"uid":126305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"整容年輕化"},{"pid":"dead5c1586afd74e0e5262f0cd871d37041b304f","tid":1029572,"uid":188050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:23:37.000Z","msg":"香港好多大超市同百貨公司都開始在童裝部賣水溶性指甲油，仲要有老母賣比小朋友喎，好快就變小學雞的潮物."},{"pid":"77a2c63deae51126df82b430c4dd07fe2cbeb5b8","tid":1029572,"uid":43042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"樓上班友屌到咁恆係咪未見過日本小學生化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc75a9788251f932b6aced1de3c1e911a1e4da2","tid":1029572,"uid":1372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a32963dac02655d221de5b589d064d3a03d84996","tid":1029572,"uid":126305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"整容年輕化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:28:22.000Z","msg":"因為18歲前唔可以整容，所以學整容術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e0b7f14335678a39da042cd2adeb9bbe8a28bf","tid":1029572,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a2c63deae51126df82b430c4dd07fe2cbeb5b8","tid":1029572,"uid":43042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"樓上班友屌到咁恆係咪未見過日本小學生化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"韓日都唔應該啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e383b714b635895f1a52d746fa55a976ebde3775","tid":1029572,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"遲早出女童用震蛋同男童用前列腺按摩棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}